        <abstract> 
<p>Greatly praises AG’s discussion of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> in <hi rend="italic">Proc. Am. Acad. Arts &amp; Sci.</hi> [4 (1860): 411–15; 424–6].</p>  
<p>Mentions other reviews of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>; believes the BAAS meeting at Oxford greatly advanced the subject. Has heard his views are gaining ground in Germany.</p> 
        </abstract>
